item.title: Wybuch Bomby w Oslo / Bomb Explosion in Oslo (Norwegia / Norway)
item.description:
Wybuch Bomby w Oslo / Bomb Explosion in Oslo (Norwegia / Norway)
Watch TV for free from your computer 24/7 - http://bitly.com/qNLLs8 Norweska policja poinformowała, że atak przybrał 'katastroficzne rozmiary". Co najmniej 84 osoby zginęły w wyniku strzelaniny na wyspie Utoya, gdzie odbywał się obóz młodzieżówki Partii Pracy premiera Jensa Stoltenberga. W wybuchu w rządowej dzielnicy w Oslo zginęło 7 osób. Policja zaapelowała, by nadal nie udawać się do centrum Oslo, by ograniczać się w rozmowach przez telefony komórkowe. Zapewniono także, że nie ma zagrożenia. Trzy osoby zostały aresztowane dziś rano w Norwegii w związku z podejrzeniem o planowanie zamachów terrorystycznych -- informuje BBC. Jak na razie nie wiadomo, czy aresztowanie mężczyzn ma związek z wybuchem, do którego doszło po południu w centrum Oslo, stolicy Norwegii.

item.title: HyunA 'Bubble POP!'
item.description:
HyunA 'Bubble POP!'
Oooh! Oh ah oh ah oh ah oooh! Hello beautiful ones! Here is a simple but HOT look for Summer. It's inspired by Kpop star, Hyuna (from 4Minute). When I first heard the song "Bubble POP", I thought it was the most annoying song ever but it somehow grew on me and now I like it lol. You have to admit that it is very catchy! I fell in love with her makeup in her promotional picture for her new single because I loved how her red sweater and her red lips POPPED. She looked so sassy and hot in a casual fun effortless way. This simple and easy look is all about glowy sun kissed skin, copper sultry eyes and hot berry lips. Although I think this look is gorgeous for Summer, it can definitely be worn all year round. This look will look great on everybody because it flatters all eye and skin colours. Note: This is just an inspired look, I am not implying I look like Hyuna. She is so HOT! Gosh, her legs *drools* Spending 18 hours flying in the air gave me a really dry patchy face. I wasn't going to film the HyunA tutorial so soon as I was waiting for my skin to regain it's moisture but I wanted to upload a tutorial before I jet off to Europe. I'm actually off to catch my flight in like an hour lol. Take care everybody and I shall speak to you all after my trip ^_^ x. _________________ Check out the Bubzbeauty Official Website.
